===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg-both|blight}}
{{wikipedia}}
# any of many [[plant]] [[disease]]s causing [[damage]] to, or the [[death]] of, [[leaf|leaves]], [[fruit]] or other parts
# the [[bacterium]], [[virus]] or [[fungus]] that causes such a condition
#(''by extension'') anything that [[impede]]s [[growth]] or [[development]] or [[spoil]]s any other [[aspect]] of [[life]]

